Style Guide

Swift Styling

view controller swift files have to end with xxxxViewController.swift
TableViewCell swift files have to end with  xxxTableViewCell.swift
xxxxController.swift should only be in xxxControllers folder. (ViewControllers swift files should only appear in ViewController folder)
References for UI’s should end up with :
label -> xxxLabel
Button -> xxxButton
Button action -> xxxButtonAction
Textfield -> xxxTf
Textfiled action -> xxxTfAction
….
Layout style is attached on GitHub repo
Images in Assets should always end up with xxx@1x, xxx@2x, xxx@3x …
All functions should have comments on them
